1.	Create A Series Using Dict In Pandas.
Ans - import pandas as pd
dic = {'a':3,'b':4,'c':7}
s=pd.Series(dic)
print(s)

2>How To Create A Copy Of The Series In Pandas?
Ans - import pandas as pd
dic = {'a':3,'b':4,'c':7}
s=pd.Series(dic)
b=s.copy()
print(b)
print(s)

